 22028	/// Evaluates B-spline basis derivatives at a single scalar point `x` into a provided buffer.
 22029	///
 22030	/// Uses the analytic de Boor derivative formula:
 22031	/// B'_{i,k}(x) = k * (B_{i,k-1}(x)/(t_{i+k}-t_i) - B_{i+1,k-1}(x)/(t_{i+k+1}-t_{i+1}))
