 13982	/// Dilogarithm `Li_2(z) = Σ_{k≥1} z^k / k²` for `z ∈ [0, 1]`.
 13983	///
 13984	/// For `z ∈ [0, 1/2]` we sum the series directly (rapid geometric decay).
 13985	/// For `z ∈ (1/2, 1]` we use the Euler reflection
